debated repeatedly during several conferences and workshop. This collection of position statements discusses related questions, such as, â€œWhat makes M&S special that we need M&S standards,â€ â€œAre M&S
standards truly different from Software Engineering Standards,â€ and â€œWhat metrics can be used to measure M&S standard success,â€ and tries to contribute to establishing a methodological approach to identify

